name: SOLIS inverter type definition
unit: definition: 0000---no definition 1010---1phase inverter 1020---3 phase inverter 2030--- 1 phase low voltage energy storage inverter

name: Inverter SN_1
remark: SN High 4 Example: (Hex) 3061 has 0x4321 3062 has 0x8765 3063 has 0xCBA9 3064 has 0x0FED The SN is 12345679ABCDEF

name: Meter Location
remark: BIT00: Meter in load BIT01: Meter in grid BIT02: 24 hour consumption BIT03: Reserved BIT04: Reserved BIT05: Reserved BIT06: Reserved BIT07-BIT15: Reserved

name: Meter PF
remark: -1.000~-0.800 +0.800~+1.000 1Ph meter: DDSD151: Actual accuracy 0.001 ACR10RD16TE:Actual accuracy0.01

name: PV1 V
remark: 101V Note ： 125K has 20 PV current，10PV voltage，1PV voltage -> 2PV current 230K series 30 strings

name: PF Setting
remark: PF： （8000.80，10001.00） （-800-0.80，-1000-1.00） （PF 1.00 same with -1.00） range（-0.80---0.80） 15KW and below don’t have this function

name: PF Setting 2
remark: PF Low： （8000.80，10001.00） （-800-0.80，-1000-1.00） （PF 1.00 same with -1.00） range（-0.80---0.80） For working mode 03 fixed pf function

name: Master/Slav e DSP
remark: 00: Master DSP upgrade 01: Slave DSP upgrade

name: Power-off saving
remark: BIT00: 0- Power off not saving 1- Power off saving

name: Get current IV curve
remark: Note: Max number is 30 Step 1: Send IV curve scanning
